highlights.text: Ari Bajgora has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Falle og slå seg” is the highest at #3.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 404 days straight.
“Byen Min (Slipknot 2026)” by SNÆX, Dape, and Nasty s is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #176.
“NOW OR NEVER” by Tkandz and CXSPER is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 58 spots at #81.
